                  <strong>Children's Hospital at Dartmouth (CHAD)</strong><br>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Comprehensive developmental evaluations</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="resource-category">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-800">ABA Therapy Providers</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                <li>
                  <strong>Moving Mountains ABA</strong><br>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Comprehensive ABA services statewide</span><br>
                  <span class="text-sm text-blue-600">Phone: (603) 555-1234</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Local ABA Providers</strong><br>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Multiple providers throughout New Hampshire</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="resource-category">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-800">Support Organizations</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                <li>
                  <strong>Autism Society of New Hampshire</strong><br>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Support, resources, and advocacy</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Parent Information Center</strong><br>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Educational advocacy and support</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>NH Family Voices</strong><br>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Family support and information</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Taking the Next Steps</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">If you're concerned about your child's development, remember that seeking evaluation and support is a sign of being a caring, proactive parent. Early intervention can make a significant difference in your child's development and your family's quality of life.</p>
          
          <div class="next-steps-list space-y-4">
            <div class="step-item flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1">1</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Talk to Your Pediatrician</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Share your concerns with your child's doctor and ask about developmental screening tools and referral options.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step-item flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1">2</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Contact Early Intervention Services</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">If your child is under 3, contact NH's Early Supports & Services program for evaluation and potential services.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step-item flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1">3</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Consider ABA Evaluation</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Contact an ABA provider like Moving Mountains ABA for a comprehensive behavioral assessment and consultation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step-item flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1">4</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Connect with Support</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Reach out to parent support groups and organizations like the Autism Society of New Hampshire for guidance and community.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Remember: You're Not Alone</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Navigating concerns about your child's development can feel overwhelming, but remember that you're not alone in this journey. New Hampshire has a strong community of families, professionals, and organizations dedicated to supporting children with autism and their families.</p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Trust your instincts as a parent. If you're concerned about your child's development, it's always better to seek evaluation and support early. Even if your child doesn't have autism, early intervention services can help with any developmental delays or challenges they may be experiencing.</p>
          
          <div class="encouragement-box bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500">
            <p class="text-lg text-blue-800 font-medium">At Moving Mountains ABA, we're here to support New Hampshire families every step of the way. Whether you need a consultation, evaluation, or ongoing ABA therapy services, our team of experienced BCBAs is committed to helping your child reach their full potential.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="cta bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Concerned About Your Child's Development?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-blue-100">Contact Moving Mountains ABA today for a free consultation. Our experienced team can help you understand your options and take the next steps toward supporting your child's development.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-blue-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
              Schedule Free Consultation
            </a>
            <a href="tel:6035551234" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors">
              Call (603) 555-1234
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

